00:15:41.650 --> 00:15:43.190
So I wasn't at
the 99-seat thing.

00:15:43.190 --> 00:15:47.910
So I guess I kind of got to
miss the hard, hard, hard part.

00:15:47.910 --> 00:15:51.830
I kind of just hopped in and
lived my life in Beverly Hills

00:15:51.830 --> 00:15:53.730
with these guys.

00:15:53.730 --> 00:15:55.880
KATIE BOECK: The
majority of the cast

00:15:55.880 --> 00:15:58.835
is almost entirely from
