00:16:10.450 --> 00:16:13.512
this is like everyone's
Broadway debut, right?

00:16:13.512 --> 00:16:14.220
KATIE BOECK: Yes.

00:16:14.220 --> 00:16:14.510
ALEX BONIELLO: Yes.

00:16:14.510 --> 00:16:15.560
ROBERT ARIZA: That's correct.

00:16:15.560 --> 00:16:17.580
ALAN SEALES: So I just want to
